==German==
===Noun===
'''Schnecke''' ''f'' (plural [[Schnecken]])

# [[snail]], [[slug]]
# (''Slang'') An [[attractive]] [[woman]]; [[chick]].
# The [[cochlea]] in the inner ear.
# A [[screw]] or [[worm]] [[thread]].
# The carved wooden spiral at the end of a stringed instrument's fingerboard.
# [[pastry]] in the form of a snail.

